at > .gitignore << 'EOF'
## Visual Studio
.vs/
bin/
obj/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Build results
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/

## .NET
*.nupkg
*.snupkg

## User-specific files
*.rsuser
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Rider
.idea/
*.sln.iml

## Temp files
*.tmp
*.temp
EOF